*** Jugs ***
// Keep your buffer clean! Make jugs without any waste.

// 1400u of Trico, primarily to make empty jugs
):Tricordrazine, BRUTE-BURN[10], POISON[5] (od0
 + 200 oxygen
 + 200 Carbon
 + 200 Sugar                = 600 Inaprovaline
oo Mix
oo Buffer                  .= 600u Inaprovaline
 + 200 silicon
 + 200 nitrogen
 + 200 potassium            = 600 Dylovene
oo Buffer                  .= 600u Inaprovaline, 200 silicon, 200 nitrogen, 200 potassium
oo Pill                    == ~20u Tricordrazine
 > 60 pills, 20u, long-teal [1~3]  // Very slightly less than 20 Trico. Also very loud

// For making jugs in the Med TecFab
):Plastic Sheets (30)
 + 30 welding fuel
 + 30 Hydrogen
 + 30 Carbon                = 90 Oil
oo Heat                     = 90 Ash
oo Buffer                  .= 90u Ash
// Be careful of beaker retaining heat. Do not use ash beaker
 + 25 welding fuel
 + 25 Hydrogen
 + 25 Carbon                = 75 Oil
oo Buffer , Repeat         .= 150u Oil, 90u Ash
 + 40 oxygen
 + 20 Hydrogen
 + 20 sulfur                = 60 sulfuric acid
oo Buffer                  .= 60u sulfuric acid, 150u Oil, 90u Ash
 + 30 Ash
 + 20 sulfuric acid
 + 50 Oil                  // Add Oil exactly, or hot Ash might burn it
oo Heat , Repeat , Repeat  == 30 Plastic
// Hot Ash might skip needing to heat the solution

*** Plants ***
// Cheat sheet for useful plants.

Aloe      >  Aloe and Dermaline. (Regenerative Mesh, Caustic, Cryo, Convinience)
Thistle   >  Stellibinin. (Poison, Caustic, Narcolepsy)
^Deus     >  Omnizine.
^Koibean  >  carpotoxin. (Cognizine)
^Trumpet  >  Polypyrylium. (Brute, Asphyx)
Lingzhi   >  Epinephrine and Ultravasculine. (Crit, Toxin)
Poppy     >  Bicaridine. (Medicated Sutures, Convinience)
Ambrosia  >  desoxyephedrine. (Security, Narcolepsy)